[{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"## `USE` statement\r\nThe `USE` statement specifies a namespace and / or a database to use for the subsequent SurrealQL statements."},{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"## Statement syntax\r\n```surrealql\r\nUSE [ NS @ns ] [ DB @db ];\r\n```"},{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"## Example usages\r\nThe following queries show example usage of this statement:"},{"kind":2,"language":"surrealql","value":"USE NS test; -- Switch to the 'test' Namespace"},{"kind":2,"language":"surrealql","value":"USE DB test; -- Switch to the 'test' Database"},{"kind":2,"language":"surrealql","value":"USE NS test DB test; -- Switch to the 'test' Namespace and 'test' Database"}]